# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Compatibility with Xcode 8 and earlier (ignoring not recommended, comment out for Xcode 8 and later)
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Compatibility with Xcode 3 and earlier (ignoring not recommended, comment out for Xcode 3 and later)
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.pbxuser
!default.pbxuser
*.mode1v3
!default.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
!default.mode2v3
*.perspectivev3
!default.perspectivev3

## Xcode Patch
*.xcodeproj/*
!*.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj
!*.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/
!*.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/
!**/*.xcworkspace/contents.xcworkspacedata
/*.gcno
**/xcshareddata/WorkspaceSettings.xcsettings

